  stimulus_text = 'The following excerpt is from a science textbook describing an experiment that involves using a magnifying glass to focus sunlight on a piece of paper.  The excerpt is written in the third person.  What is the best way to rewrite this excerpt to be written in the first person? Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
